OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with rain, some
OL,6,Fthundery, at first. Drier and brighter
OL,7,Fconditions spread north during the
OL,8,Fmorning. Further cloud and patchy rain
OL,9,Fwill follow north from mid-afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThe night will stay mostly
OL,12,Fcloudy, patchy rain during the evening
OL,13,Fwill become more widespread and heavy
OL,14,Fat times after midnight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSunday:FCloudy with locally heavy rain
OL,17,Fat times during the morning. The
OL,18,Fafternoon will become brighter as the
OL,19,Frain clears north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
