OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,6,Fspells with showery rain Monday
OL,7,Fbecoming cloudy but drier Tuesday.
OL,8,FOutbreaks of heavy rain push northeast
OL,9,Ffrom Wednesday afternoon.
